</p>

<p>
Now we are prepared to assemble the pieces and generate the graph of the piecewise-defined function

<me>g(t) = \left\{
	\begin{array}{ll}
		0,		\amp t \lt 1		\\
		t^2,	\amp 1 \le t \lt 2	\\
		-t+1,	\amp 2 \le t \lt 6	\\
		0,		\amp t \ge 6		\\
	\end{array} \right.
</me>
</p>

